lead_paragraph: Australian Daniel Ricciardo seized the first pole position of his Formula One career at the Monaco Grand Prix on Saturday with world championship leader Nico Rosberg joining him on the front row for Mercedes.

headline.print_headline: Ricciardo Takes First F1 Pole in Monaco
headline.main: Ricciardo Takes First F1 Pole in Monaco
